html vertical centering
from http://apptools.com/examples/tableheight.php

Now that we have achieved 100% height with our table, it becomes a simple matter to center content. Let's take the following CSS:

   html, body, #wrapper {
      height:100%;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      border: none;
      text-align: center;
   }
   #wrapper {
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: middle;
      width: 400px;
   }
    

Use the above CSS along with the following HTML:

   <body>
   <table id="wrapper">
      <tr>
         <td>This is centered</td>
      </tr>
   </table>
   </body>
